			<h1>Matthew<br /><span class="accent-text">Windham</span></h1>
			<p class="tagline">Infrastructure automation, AWS migrations, and reliability engineering.</p>

			<div class="cta-row">
				<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/resume">View Resume</a>
				<a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/about">About Me</a>
			</div>

			<div class="contact-row">
				<a href="https://github.com/fattswindstorm" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="GitHub">
